= window label "Attribute: Mode"
+ header label "Attribute: Mode"
+ subheader label "Description"
+ text label "The mode attribute is used to describe the state of a widget."
+ subheader label "Syntax"
+ code label "mode <state>"
+ list id arguments
+ text in arguments label "state: The state of can either be off, on or disabled"
+ subheader label "Example"
+ code label "+ toggle label \"Lights!\" mode \"on\""
